## About BICES

BICES (Beijing International Construction Machinery Exhibition & Seminar) is one of the world's largest exhibitions for construction and mining machinery. Held in Beijing, China, this massive trade fair attracts over 150,000 visitors and 1,200+ exhibitors from around the globe.

## Exhibition Scope

- Construction Machinery and Equipment
- Mining Machinery and Technology
- Road Construction Equipment
- Concrete and Cement Machinery
- Material Handling Equipment
- Parts and Components

## Event Scale

As one of the "Big Five" construction equipment exhibitions globally, BICES provides unparalleled access to the Chinese market and Asian construction industry. The exhibition spans multiple halls showcasing the latest innovations from leading international and Chinese manufacturers.

## Why Attend?

Access the world's largest construction equipment market, meet with Chinese buyers and distributors, discover Asian manufacturing innovations, and establish business relationships in the rapidly growing Asian construction and mining sectors.
